# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# 1) Canonicalize legacy English-prefixed URLs
/en         /               301
/en/        /               301
/en/*       /:splat         301

# 2) Legacy locale code migrations
/fil        /tl             301
/fil/*      /tl/:splat      301
/no         /nb             301
/no/*       /nb/:splat      301

# 3) Static assets are served directly from dist by Pages.
# Do not rewrite extension paths like /*.png -> /:splat,
# otherwise requests become /file (extension stripped) and 404.

# 4) SPA fallback (enable only if needed for non-prerendered routes)
# /*        /index.html      200
